Note on the bundled data: the files under data/ and results/ are derived from
the 2Inspire study and are fully anonymized (participant labels P1..P29; no
PII). They are provided for reproducibility and illustration. Raw physiological
recordings are not distributed. Please cite the project (see CITATION.cff) if
you use the code or data in academic work.
